        /></a>
        <div class="book-desc">
          <h2>The Lost Apothecary</h2>
          <p>
            A female apothecary secretly dispenses poisons to liberate women
            from the men who have wronged them—setting three lives across
            centuries on a dangerous collision course.Rule #1: The poison must
            never be used to harm another woman. Rule #2: The names of the
            murderer and her victim must be recorded in the apothecary’s
            register.
          </p>
        </div>
